GtkHTML-3.27.1 2009-05-04
--------------------------

Bug Fixes:
	#494986 - Do not block view update when cursor changed in any frame of the whole hierarchy.
	#581228 - tarball does not provide gtkhtml-editor
	#580946 - Remove usage of deprecated gtk api
	#494986 - Do not centre to cursor position on click over URL and draw event.
	#571743 - Kill the deprecated html-editor component and remove any trace of it from the build files.  Buh bye, Bonobo.
	#576684 - implement pixel sized font units in gtk_html_set_fonts and html_painter_alloc_font
	#574335 - Use a proper format string ("%s") for g_warning.
	#573046 - Get rid of deprecated GTK_CHECK_*

Updated Translations:
	MiloÅ¡ PopoviÄ (sr)
	Amitakhya Phukan(as)
	Shankar Prasad (kn)
	Djihed Afifi(ar)
	Ignacio Casal Quinteiro(gl)


GtkHTML-3.26.0 2009-03-16
--------------------------

This release has no major features, but just bug fixes & updated translations. See 
the individual release NEWS entries for exact bug numbers and fixes.

